


About
-----

Satellite Orbit Simulator using TLE data from NORAD.



Prerequisites
-------------

CMake - Cross-platform build tool
GLEW  - The OpenGL extension wrangler
GLFW  - Toolkit for creating OpenGL contexts, handling input, etc...
glm   - GL math library



Building
--------

$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -H. -Bbuild/debug
$ cd build/debug

OR

$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -H. -Bbuild/release
$ cd build/release

$ make -j4

$ env CTEST_OUTPUT_ON_FAILURE=1 make test



Installing
----------

$ make install

This will install to the top-level project directory but can be over-ridden:

$ make DESTDIR=/some/prefix/path install



